<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#906a4d790d79411909b49177c242aa06>.
<#906a4d790d79411909b49177c242aa06> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/90a1b29c-5a9f-4bc4-b26a-3d08611c0940>;
