}

<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#b7c61ec04faf397f9dca7da000652334>.
<#b7c61ec04faf397f9dca7da000652334> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/617a59fa-087b-4416-83df-486b85dcb1ed>;
