<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#cb30a4823ff530bf98341acbc602875d>.
<#cb30a4823ff530bf98341acbc602875d> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/d8ec2980-752c-11ed-a51b-432755aaeed3>;
