_:b0__36029 <http://www.w3.org/ns/locn#geometry> "POLYGON((-4.10 65.90,30.20 65.90,30.20 48.50,-4.10 48.50,-4.10 65.90))"^^<http://www.opengis.net/ont/geosparql#wktLiteral>;
