    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#agent> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/818/resource/bbb9c34030836590dd6616d681cbb0f2>;
    a <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#Attribution>.
<https://doi.org/10.5878/teyk-ej56> <http://purl.org/dc/terms/accessRights> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/access-right/NON_PUBLIC>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/language> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/language/ENG>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2021003153>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "The aim of the study was to identify spatial transcriptomic and proteomic differences between thymic tissue from patients with 22q11.2 deletion syndrome and controls. Thymic tissue from two patients with 22q11DS and eight controls were subject to spatial transcriptomics and proteomics using Visium and Phenocycler methodologies, respectively.\n\nThe dataset contains data from the manuscript \"Fibroblast-driven collagen expansion and altered thymic medullary niches in 22q11.2 deletion syndrome\" by Hennings et al, which was submitted for publication in February 2026."@en, "Syftet med studien var att identifiera skillnader avseende spatiala transkriptom och proteom mellan tymusvävnad från patienter med 22q11.2-deletionssyndrom och kontroller. Tymusvävnad från två patienter med 22q11DS och åtta kontroller analyserades med spatial transkriptomik och proteomik med hjälp av Visium- respektive Phenocycler-metodik.\n\nDatasetet innehåller data från manuskriptet ”Fibroblast-driven collagen expansion and altered thymic medullary niches in 22q11.2 deletion syndrome” av Hennings et al., som skickades in för publicering i februari 2026."@sv;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/spatial> <http://sws.geonames.org/2661886>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#distribution> <https://doi.org/10.5878/teyk-ej56#distribution>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/issued> "2026-04-16T13:11:36.816524Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#landingPage> <https://doi.org/10.5878/teyk-ej56>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/modified> "2026-04-16T13:11:36.816524Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Data for: Fibroblast-driven collagen expansion and altered thymic medullary niches in 22q11.2 deletion syndrome"@en, "Data för: Fibroblast-driven collagen expansion and altered thymic medullary niches in 22q11.2 deletion syndrome"@sv;
