<https://opendata-api.malmo.se/dataset/00b1590e-a504-4c55-a7f2-3d6fd659d982> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://admin.dataportal.se/store/290/resource/abd7da407bcfbc956fd6c0e91189412f>;
