<#52540296d5a5407e53e66b4101d6a7bb> {
<https://doi.org/10.23695/Q1FY-TG26> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "Language Technology (Computational Linguistics)"@en, "lexicon"@en;
