    a <http://purl.org/dc/terms/Location>.
<https://resources.stockholm.se/data/8d31bae2-c317-48a0-961e-bc7192e150d4> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#contactPoint> <https://resources.stockholm.se/metadata#vcard/Stockholms+stad+-+Trafikkontoret/>;
